  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的风险响应流程图。核心是从MQTT Broker开始，根据风险等级分流到不同的处理节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Broker作为起点。那风险等级具体怎么划分？我需要知道分流的判断逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分三级：高风险走PLC逻辑，中高风险走边缘节点，中低风险直接进遥测数据流。Broker后面要放一个判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Broker连到判断节点，然后三条分支分别标注高、中高、中低。PLC逻辑、边缘节点、遥测流作为三个并行路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但三条路径最终要汇合。PLC逻辑和边缘节点处理完后，也要进入同一个遥测数据流，然后再统一回到PLC逻辑做最终响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：Broker→判断节点→三条分支→PLC/边缘/遥测→三者都汇入第二个遥测节点→最后回到PLC逻辑。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。注意这里有两个遥测流节点，一个是中低风险直接进的，另一个是汇合后统一的出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了初稿。起点是MQTT Broker，菱形判断节点分出高、中高、中低三条线，三个处理节点，然后汇聚到第二个遥测流，最后指向PLC逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，判断节点的画法不对。你画成了Broker直接连到三个节点，但判断节点本身应该是独立的菱形，从Broker出来先进判断节点，再分流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，Broker→菱形判断→三条分支。我调整一下，把判断节点独立出来，Broker只连到这一个判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有，中低风险那条分支是直接进第一个遥测流，但PLC逻辑和边缘节点处理完之后要汇入第二个遥测流，不是直接连回PLC。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在结构是：Broker→判断节点→三条分支（高→PLC逻辑，中高→边缘节点，中低→遥测流1），然后PLC逻辑和边缘节点都连到遥测流2，遥测流1也连到遥测流2，最后遥测流2连到PLC逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "遥测流1和遥测流2其实是同一个类型的节点吗？还是两个独立的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "按你的描述，中低风险直接进遥测流，另外两条路径处理完也进遥测流。我理解这是两个阶段：一个是原始数据入口，一个是处理后汇总出口。但Mermaid里节点名相同会合并，需要区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不用区分，就是同一个遥测流概念，表示数据最终都进入统一的遥测通道。但流程上画成两个节点更清楚：一个是直接接入点，一个是汇总后的出口。不过既然Mermaid会合并，那就用一个节点F表示遥测流，从B的中低分支直接到F，C和D也连到F。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终结构确认：A(MQTT Broker)→B{判断节点}，B分三高/中高/中低到C(PLC逻辑)/D(边缘节点)/E(遥测流)，然后C→F、D→F、E→F，最后F→G(PLC逻辑)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，E和F都是遥测流，但E是B的中低分支直接连的，F是C、D、E共同汇入后的节点，最后G是最终的PLC响应逻辑。这样风险响应的完整闭环就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
